def: To take off the slings of, as a yard, a cask, or the like; torelease from the slings. Totten.
The goddess of fruits and fruit trees.
The art of, or method for, assisting the memory by associatingthe thing or subject to be remembered with some place. [R.]
The separation of the parts of a compound word by theintervention of one or more words; as, in what place soever, forwhatsoever place.
A west Indian plant of the genus Maranta, esp. M. arundinacea,now cultivated in many hot countries. It said that the Indians usedthe roots to neutralize the venom in wounds made by poisoned arrows.
Act of dispanding, or state of being dispanded. [Obs.]
One who, or that which, rids.
